  281. 281  function addKeyboardNavigation(){
  282. 282   var tableElm, cells, settings;
  283. 283  
  284. 284   cells = tinyMCEPopup.dom.select(".charmaplink", "charmapgroup");
  285. 285  
  286. 286   settings ={
  287. 287   root: "charmapgroup",
  288. 288   items: cells
  289. 289   };
  290. 290  
  291. 291   tinyMCEPopup.editor.windowManager.createInstance('tinymce.ui.KeyboardNavigation', settings, tinyMCEPopup.dom);
  292. 292  }
  293. 293  
  294. 294  function renderCharMapHTML() {
  295. 295   var charsPerRow = 20, tdWidth=20, tdHeight=20, i;
  296. 296   var html = '<div id="charmapgroup" aria-labelledby="charmap_label" tabindex="0" role="listbox">'+
  297. 297   '<table role="presentation" border="0" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="0" width="' + (tdWidth*charsPerRow) +
  298. 298   '"><tr height="' + tdHeight + '">';
  299. 299   var cols=-1;
  300. 300  
  301. 301   for (i=0; i<charmap.length; i++) {
  302. 302   var previewCharFn;
  303. 303  
  304. 304   if (charmap[i][2]==true) {
  305. 305   cols++;
  306. 306   previewCharFn = 'previewChar(\'' + charmap[i][1].substring(1,charmap[i][1].length) + '\',\'' + charmap[i][0].substring(1,charmap[i][0].length) + '\',\'' + charmap[i][3] + '\');';
  307. 307   html += ''
  308. 308   + '<td class="charmap">'
  309. 309   + '<a class="charmaplink" role="button" onmouseover="'+previewCharFn+'" onfocus="'+previewCharFn+'" href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="insertChar(\'' + charmap[i][1].substring(2,charmap[i][1].length-1) + '\');" onclick="return false;" onmousedown="return false;" title="' + charmap[i][3] + '">'
  310. 310   + charmap[i][1]
  311. 311   + '</a></td>';
  312. 312   if ((cols+1) % charsPerRow == 0)
  313. 313   html += '</tr><tr height="' + tdHeight + '">';
  314. 314   }
  315. 315   }
  316. 316  
  317. 317   if (cols % charsPerRow > 0) {
  318. 318   var padd = charsPerRow - (cols % charsPerRow);
  319. 319   for (var i=0; i<padd-1; i++)
  320. 320   html += '<td width="' + tdWidth + '" height="' + tdHeight + '" class="charmap">&nbsp;</td>';
  321. 321   }
  322. 322  
  323. 323   html += '</tr></table></div>';
  324. 324   html = html.replace(/<tr height="20"><\/tr>/g, '');
  325. 325  
  326. 326   return html;
  327. 327  }
  328. 328  
  329. 329  function insertChar(chr) {
  330. 330   tinyMCEPopup.execCommand('mceInsertContent', false, '&#' + chr + ';');
  331. 331  
  332. 332   // Refocus in window
  333. 333   if (tinyMCEPopup.isWindow)
  334. 334   window.focus();
  335. 335  
  336. 336   tinyMCEPopup.editor.focus();
  337. 337   tinyMCEPopup.close();
  338. 338  }
  339. 339  
  340. 340  function previewChar(codeA, codeB, codeN) {
  341. 341   var elmA = document.getElementById('codeA');
  342. 342   var elmB = document.getElementById('codeB');
  343. 343   var elmV = document.getElementById('codeV');
  344. 344   var elmN = document.getElementById('codeN');
  345. 345  
  346. 346   if (codeA=='#160;') {
  347. 347   elmV.innerHTML = '__';
  348. 348   } else {
  349. 349   elmV.innerHTML = '&' + codeA;
  350. 350   }
  351. 351  
  352. 352   elmB.innerHTML = '&amp;' + codeA;
  353. 353   elmA.innerHTML = '&amp;' + codeB;
  354. 354   elmN.innerHTML = codeN;
  355. 355  }
